items.title: Amplify
items.description:
https://github.com/sharathdoes/Amplify

Amplify is an innovative platform designed to fill a crucial gap in the job market by offering a dedicated referral system for qualified candidates. Unlike traditional job platforms, Amplify focuses on connecting eligible job seekers with referral opportunities. Using advanced machine learning models and tailored assessments, Amplify evaluates users' skills and qualifications. Upon successfully passing these assessments, candidates receive referrals from industry professionals, offering a direct and trusted pathway to employment.

items.title: Anomaly Detection and Notification System
items.description:
https://github.com/sharathdoes/Anomaly-Detection-and-Notification-System

This project is designed to detect anomalies from an IP camera feed, save the anomaly frames, and send notifications via SMS using Twilio. Additionally, it serves the saved anomaly frames through a server.

We trained a model using the I3D (Inflated 3D) architecture on the UCF Crime Dataset, which is available here. The resulting trained model (win.h5) is used in this project to detect anomalies in real-time from an IP camera feed.

items.title: StudySphere
items.description:
StudySphere: an innovative AI-powered interactive quiz platform designed to empower users with seamless quiz generation capabilities, whether based on specific topics or uploaded PDF documents.


Key Features:
- Explore various quizzing modes, including Timer Mode, Quiz Mode, and No Limit Mode, catering to diverse learning preferences.
 - Generate quizzes effortlessly based on preferred topics, uploaded PDF text content, or manual inputs.
 - Enjoy centralized management of all created quizzes within the user interface.
 - Foster friendly competition by challenging other users with shared quizzes via WhatsApp.
 - Stay engaged with dynamic leaderboards for each quiz, fueling a competitive spirit.
 - Connect with friends for instant quiz sharing and collaboration.
 - Seamlessly communicate with friends through the platform's built-in messaging feature.
 - Experience scalable quiz generation with a token-based system; users can refill tokens conveniently through the Razorpay gateway when needed.
 - Join us in revolutionizing the way quizzes are crafted and shared, making learning an interactive and enjoyable experience for all.

Live: https://studysphere-ai.vercel.app
